cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.IT, cs.OH, cs.MM

The paper presents a computational camera for 3D imaging, which involves computer vision and graphics techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optics and imaging, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses compressed sensing, which is a topic in information theory and could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper provides new theory for analyzing resolution in computational cameras, which could fall under cs.OH (Other Computer Science).
